Welcome to "cutparty_LL_01"

Map created By El_Mexicano


This is an CUT/KNIFE map(your only weapon will be the KNIFE on that map) , with 32 slots in each team for a total of 64 slots 

Very fun and speed map , there is many like "sky jump" will make you move faster and higher and will permit you to access many plateform and 
part of the map faster , bu tbe carefull because the sky jump can just as well help you to go higher and faster but can also kill you if you
fail your jump ;-)
there is too a yellow central plateform sliding & see trought which help you to see what's happen under in the small labyrinth !!!
Ambiant musique and originals sounds in that map too .


The .BSP file makes 2,5 MO.

Big thanks to the Los Latinos production for their help & all the Los latinos team for the help they gave me
